LmCommon
========

This repository contains code that is shared among Lifemapper components.

We acknowledge the support of grant BIO/EF #0851290 from the U.S. National Science Foundation for the production of this software.

-----

Configuration
=============
Set an environment variable, $LIFEMAPPER_CONFIG_FILE, that points to your 
configuration file.  Some default configuration files are provided with the 
other components.  Edit those files to match your environment.



Installation
============
The Lifemapper Client Library (LmClient) can be installed using setuptools.  It
has been tested with Python 2.7 and requires 
LmCommon (https://github.com/lifemapper/LmCommon).  You can install it by 
unzipping the package and using the standard build and install 
(https://docs.python.org/2/install/#standard-build-and-install).

`
python setup.py build
python setup.py install
`
